  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Psychosocial and soco-pastoral support for families affected by Easter Sunday bombings</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will provide psychosocial support, immediate relief through cash vouchers, medical and travel assistance to persons bereaved, physically injured or otherwise affected by the Easter bombings.  110 families will be provided with livelihood assistance, and legal assistance will be given where needed eg for documentation and transfer of assets following family deaths.</narrative>
  </description>
